result.name: Sushi Wadatsumi

reviews.text: Expensive. Some of the best sushi I've ever had, including in Japan. Nice, simple decor. Polite, attentive staff. It felt like we could have been in Japan.

The chef gets all the details right. Choices of fish is remarkably good. If you like high standard sushi in a casual and relaxing setting, this is the place for you. Lunch set is a good bargain and good as an entry point. The place is usually not fully packed, but given the small number of seats I recommend you to book ahead.
One of the best sushi I ever had.. And I eat usually a lot of sushi in nice places
The rice was so over salted I suffered with salty mouth for the rest of the day. Prices crazy. Empty restaurant.
Great omakase in HK, price is not cheap though

reviews.text: 在夏天品嚐許多美味的貝類，食材處理的很好；惟壽司醋飯和魚的味道並沒有融合在一起，有點可惜。
Expensive. Some of the best sushi I've ever had, including in Japan. Nice, simple decor. Polite, attentive staff. It felt like we could have been in Japan.

The chef gets all the details right. Choices of fish is remarkably good. If you like high standard sushi in a casual and relaxing setting, this is the place for you. Lunch set is a good bargain and good as an entry point. The place is usually not fully packed, but given the small number of seats I recommend you to book ahead.
雖然好貴，但是味道和賣相都是酒店級，值得一嘗
いやあ、香港でこんなに美味い寿司が食べられるとは思ってもみませんでした。伊達にミシュラン獲得してないですね。800HKDのランチセットでしたが、何もかもがパーフェクトでした。ガリも美味すぎて3回くらいお代わりｗやっぱある程度カネ出せば、こんなに美味いもん食べれるんだね。。これから旦那のボーナス出るたびにこちらに伺うことになりそうです(*^^*)
